Founder of Rapture Proclaimer Evangelical Church of God, Evangelist Funmilayo Adebayo popularly known as Mummy G.O, has revealed that the person behind the anonymous voice of Big Brother in the Big Brother Naija reality tv is Lucifer. The controversial cleric disclosed this in video while speaking to the congregation in her church, expressing that his anonymous and mysterious facade is due to the fact the he is a satani She said, “Who is Big Brother? The people that watch it, I am talking to you. Who is Big Brother? Lucifer. Angel Smith Lists Out All Of Her Achievements At 21. “Don’t Get Married Or Have Kids If You Are Broke”- Ifu Ennada “Throughout that programme you will never see his face, have they ever show the face of Big Brother before? They won’t show his face and he will be talking to them. He will be telling them ‘I am watching you’. “You know they make us believe that there are cameras everywhere, they make us believe that. I pity you, this is how the whole world will live under the kingdom of anti-Christ.”